  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Exceptional Wireless Capabilities",
      "text": "Experience the future of networking with the MikroTik RB4011iGS+5HacQ2HnD-IN, a groundbreaking router designed for exceptional connectivity and performance. With a powerful Quad-core 1.4GHz CPU and 1GB of RAM, this router ensures outstanding performance in every task."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Exceptional Wireless Capabilities",
      "text": "The RB4011iGS+5HacQ2HnD-IN offers exceptional wireless capabilities, supporting dual-band 2.4GHz/5GHz 4x4 MIMO 802.11a/b/g/n/ac technology. Experience high-speed wireless connectivity with a radio rate of 300Mbps in the 2.4GHz band and an impressive 1.7Gbps in the 5GHz band. This router's omni antenna design and wide frequency range spanning 2.412 - 2.484GHz and 5.150 - 5.875GHz ensure reliable connections across various landscapes."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Exceptional Wireless Capabilities",
      "text": "",
      "media": [
        {
          "url": "https://www.getic.com/images/catalogue/description/826/series_banner-64e6000571a7c-1780x540.jpg",
          "alt": "/images/catalogue/description/826/series_banner-64e6000571a7c-1780x540.jpg",
          "type": "image"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "Simplified Network Setup",
      "text": "Elevate your network infrastructure with the RB4011iGS+5HacQ2HnD-IN, enclosed in a professional matte black metal casing. Its 10 Gigabit ports ensure rapid data transmission, making it ideal for high-demand LAN connectivity. Additionally, the 10Gbps SFP+ cage provides a seamless avenue for gigabit-speed fiber connectivity, offering versatility for diverse networking demands. One standout feature is the PoE output on port #10, which adds a new dimension of flexibility to your network setup. Whether you're setting up IP phones, surveillance systems, or wireless access points, this router simplifies your infrastructure, reduces the need for extra power sources, and streamlines complex cabling arrangements, resulting in cost savings and efficient operations."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Simplified Network Setup",
      "text": "",
      "media": [
        {
          "url": "https://www.getic.com/images/catalogue/description/826/group32-64e6000a10621-1300x540.jpg",
          "alt": "/images/catalogue/description/826/group32-64e6000a10621-1300x540.jpg",
          "type": "image"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "Resilient Power Management",
      "text": "Efficiency and adaptability are at the core of the RB4011iGS+5HacQ2HnD-IN's design. Thanks to its ARM CPU architecture, the device achieves a maximum power consumption of 23 watts; which is highly efficient for its performance, reducing operational costs and minimizing heat generation. The router's versatility shines through its support for multiple power methods, including AC/DC Adapter, 24V Passive PoE, and 48V Passive PoE. This adaptability ensures seamless operations in various environments, from standard office setups to challenging indoor locations with fluctuating power supplies."
    }
